<body>
    <div class="container">

        <div class="main">
            <h1 class="welcome">Welcome to Daily Journal</h1>

            <div class="create-blog">
                <h2>Create a Blog</h2>
                <p class="main-content">Share your unique story and stand out in the vast world of adventures. Join us
                    now
                    to ensure your
